time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
explanation: The solution uses a two-pointer approach, starting from both ends of the string. It iteratively removes matching prefixes and suffixes, resulting in an efficient linear time complexity. The space complexity is constant as it only uses a fixed amount of space.

